      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJESTIC GA GA (7) added to the impressive sequence of wins last start when she scored by a neck over 2503m at this track. Interesting to see what unfolds from this wide draw. Tackles a similar assignment and she can go right on with the job. MRIYA DREAM (2) finished seventh last start over 2185m at Pinjarra, beaten 18 metres, after filling a minor placing at the previous appearance over 1684m there. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Meets a comparable field and he can play a big role. ALDEBARAN BOYD (4) is capable of better after finishing well back when resuming over 2116m at Pinjarra two weeks ago. Strips fitter now. LINE THE STARZZZ (3) is the best of the rest after finishing runner-up over 2130m at this course last time out. Include from the low draw.",
